12::[Adventures]::
2Adventures are the main system of this game where players will party together to explore areas and fight monsters.  If they are successful they will walk away from the adventure with experience and loot.
12::[Adventure Actions]::
2Once inside an adventure the party leader will have access to a variety of different commands. Note that most of these commands consume party stamina.  If the party runs out of stamina the adventure will end in a failure. Stamina can be checked with !stamina
12::[Action List ]::
2This is a list of all adventure actions that can be done by the party leader. For more info use 12!help <!command>2 to read more about it.
2!look, !go, !rest, !warp, !push, !pull, !read, !open, !close, !chop tree, !mine